      "content": "i tried the privileged flag and the overlay2 thing but it didnt change anything, still panicking. and i dont even have a GPU in this workstation so the cuda stuff is irrelevant. the dmesg logs are a mess because they stop so abruptly. i'm really stressed, i can't keep troubleshooting these random settings. can you just find a definitive way to stop the crash so i can close this ticket and get back to work? i just need it to work now.",
